{"tid":1937615,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"BBC總整理，一次看完疫情爆發以來WHO 秘書長譚德塞「名言佳句」特輯：往反面去想就對了","createTime":"2020-03-22T04:55:39.000Z","updateTime":"2020-03-24T10:48:33.000Z","uid":178875,"like":144,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":42,"replies":[{"pid":"632c081fcc026008f7847287b732a65ec361bf0f","tid":1937615,"uid":178875,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-22T04:55:39.000Z","msg":"武漢肺炎（新型冠狀病毒肺炎）疫情從去年年底開始傳出，我國在今年一月時就已超前部署展開對策會議，反觀 WHO 一直以來傾向採取消極不作為方式任由疫情肆虐。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn0.techbang.com/system/images/549263/original/579f6f192963be8843613aaf23595cd4.jpg?1584508308\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn0.techbang.com%2Fsystem%2Fimages%2F549263%2Foriginal%2F579f6f192963be8843613aaf23595cd4.jpg%3F1584508308&h=79f5360e&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n英國廣播公司 BBC 就整理了 WHO 秘書長譚德塞自疫情爆發以來的各種金句：<br />\n<br />\n<strong>1 月 23 日<br />\n<br />\n「中國分享疫情信息非常及時，即時採取相應措施，展現出相當高的透明度。」</strong><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn1.techbang.com/system/images/549264/original/3064cd769f67d2f78f8b792fd418a3cd.jpg?1584508309\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn1.techbang.com%2Fsystem%2Fimages%2F549264%2Foriginal%2F3064cd769f67d2f78f8b792fd418a3cd.jpg%3F1584508309&h=1663d486&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<strong>2 月 11 日<br />\n<br />\n「中國以外的疫情傳播可能『冰山一角』⋯⋯必須團結對抗病毒，確保疫情不會失控。」<br />\n2 月 12 日<br />\n<br />\n「比起恐怖襲擊，病毒能引發政治經濟文化動盪的威力更大⋯⋯國際應該更積極對抗疫情，把這項病毒視為頭號公敵。」<br />\n2 月 21 日<br />\n<br />\n「中國新型肺炎新增病例持續減少，趨勢令人鼓舞。」</strong><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn0.techbang.com/system/images/549266/original/7d229cceb8df82f297d7b01819bcf161.jpg?1584508313\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn0.techbang.com%2Fsystem%2Fimages%2F549266%2Foriginal%2F7d229cceb8df82f297d7b01819bcf161.jpg%3F1584508313&h=77e36aae&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<strong>2 月 24 日<br />\n<br />\n「現在使用大流行一詞不符合事實，肯定會引起恐慌。」<br />\n3 月 2 日<br />\n<br />\n世界衛生組織再次表示：「2019 冠狀病毒疫情（武漢肺炎）仍未構成全球大流行。」</strong><br />\n3 月 11 日<br />\n<br />\n世界衛生組織正式宣佈：「2019 新型冠狀病毒肺炎（武漢肺炎）成為大流行疾病。」<br />\n<br />\n從現在看來，WHO 秘書長譚德塞所說的話幾乎都已成為了反面實例，例如：中國抗疫訊息展現了相當高的透明度（最後因防疫不透明導致全球大流行）；反對任何中國旅遊與貿易限制（實際上限制才能有效防疫，沒有限制的國家全都造成大流行）；使用大流行一詞不符合現實（沒有預防大流行的舉措，任由疫情肆虐）。<br />\n<br />\nSource: <a href=\"https://www.techbang.com/posts/76989\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.techbang.com%2Fposts%2F76989&d=HaOdbOSPDN3vR1kWeckjcMvW%2Fvk9QtnWk1JKGKfj%2Fbg%3D&h=e07b2bae\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.techbang.com/posts/76989</a><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/bbcnewstrad/videos/640272586539454/?v=640272586539454\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2Fbbcnewstrad%2Fvideos%2F640272586539454%2F%3Fv%3D640272586539454&d=HaOdbOSPDN3vR1kWeckjcMvW%2Fvk9QtnWk1JKGKfj%2Fbg%3D&h=13ba3404\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/bbcnewstrad/videos/640272586539454/?v=640272586539454</a>"},{"pid":"ca547a9219a1f89a258a5c6e5deda7cc03d018ec","tid":1937615,"uid":158613,"like":66,"dislike":0,"score":66,"citedBy":4,"replyTime":"2020-03-22T05:01:24.000Z","msg":"條黑柴已經係個死人"},{"pid":"dd1c2a5edd48dd261618a017930e376363e2fab2","tid":1937615,"uid":19552,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-24T00:05:11.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4f5845389858814744228751289a40b214ae4ec9","tid":1937615,"uid":42751,"like":18,"dislike":3,"score":15,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-24T00:07:46.000Z","msg":"fucking nigger"},{"pid":"323c30a04ad7d0c9bfc9e689791f95a5ff67a87b","tid":1937615,"uid":11980,"like":12,"dislike":0,"score":12,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-03-24T00:09:12.000Z","msg":"替死鬼黎 應該集中火力要求中共賠錢俾各國先岩"},{"pid":"005109ba1347827c01dcba28cab4af89156fb3e7","tid":1937615,"uid":11454,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-03-24T00:09:47.000Z","msg":"依個人天皇都保佢唔到， 好快變condom"},{"pid":"42d4868bd153ac91e40d92c84716c4fb4e3a7583","tid":1937615